<p class="header1"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Research 
  Interests</font></p>
<blockquote> 
  <p class="testopiccolo"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">My 
    research activity involves the area of distributed systems. My main interest is devising
    distributed algorithms achieving communication/coordination in large scale network, i.e. 
    protocols exhibiting properties like scalability, robustness, reliability despite of failures, 
    sporadic connectivity, dynamic changes. In particular I'm focusing on  
    communication paradigms  that provide an "anonymous" communication as publish/subscribe, shared memories.     
     </font></p>
    <p class="testopiccolo"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
    My early works involved the issue of fault-tolerance in asynchronous systems 
    (software replication in three-tier architectures).
</font></p>
</blockquote>
